content: Docked one star, could not eat the ecosystem. Otherwise fishy classic is a faithful recreation of the original Web game.

Played on a web browser long ago. Those new are going to complain. In short, if you've returned, good for us. If you're new and just want to complain instead of playing it on the web, on behalf of f*** y*u airlines, go f*** yourself.
Still a nice game, but the input lags and doesn't detect every movement well
The controls don't work very well, takes the fun out of it.

For all the people complaining about this game, (the joystick doesn't work, you can't tell which fish to eat, I'm just going to complain and criticize this game because its too hard for me...); this game was created long before most of you were even born, and yes, the controls are difficult, and yes, it is tough to tell which fish you can and can't eat sometimes, that is the whole point! This game is actually a challenge to play and beat. WARNING: THIS GAME IS NOT FOR MILLENNIALS
It's a good game but the controls really arent good. You cant tell which fish you can and cant eat without risk of being eaten.
Wasting Money to purchase this Game. Joystick not working properly ..
Poor controls.
Controls suck. I've lost so many times because the controls don't work properly. Increase the sensitivity or something. Paid for this game and its frustrating that the controls suck
The joystick option doesn't work properly. Need a lot of improvement. Playing from OnePlus 5
The control for my Moto g4 is very stiff
Why the hell isn't there an option to silence the music?!
joy stick is terrible
Love this game, but do not enjoy the joystick controls. Would prefer the option to switch to motion controlled. If that gets included in the game, would give 5 stars
controls are far too spotty to recommend
childhood game
Garbage controls
The joystick is completely jacked up. When I try to move the fish, the joy stick will not appear and you are stuck when you needed to move. Complete lack of effort of the developers part.
Just needs more control options, set joystick, d pad etc. Then it would be perfect
Amazing just like I remember

If you are looking for the fishy game you played on the internet, this it 
exactly it!! Controlled with a joystick anywhere you place, once you adapt 
to it, its hours of endless fun!!
